com.datamelt.rules.parser.xml

Class RowDefinitionParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • com.datamelt.rules.parser.xml.RowDefinitionParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.xml.sax.ContentHandler, org.xml.sax.DTDHandler, org.xml.sax.EntityResolver, org.xml.sax.ErrorHandler

    public class RowDefinitionParser
extends org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
implements org.xml.sax.ContentHandler
    this parser is used to parse row definition files. these describe how a fixed length ASCII file is constructed in regards to its fields. the file has to be written using the syntax as documented.
    Author:
    uwe geercken
